-- 2010-10-01T18:37:56Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-01/ex-astronaut-mccandless-sues-dido-for-using-space-flight-picture-on-album.html
Former NASA astronaut Bruce
McCandless sued the artist Dido, saying she didn’t have his
permission to use a photograph of his 1984 space flight for the
cover of her 2008 album “Safe Trip Home.”  To contact the reporter on this story:
Edvard Pettersson in Los Angeles at 
 epettersson@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
